references: Related: CF 277202; Supersedes: Res 24179; Amends: Ord 91910
summary: AN ORDINANCE amending Section 21.18.060 of the Traffic Code (Ordinance 91910) to establish a twenty-five miles per hour maximum speed limit upon Fauntleroy Way Southwest from California Avenue Southwest to Southwest Trenton Street, and superseding Resolution 24179 to the extent in conflict.
